{
  "stem": "26790.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Everything, every detail I was mentioned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Oh, war without declaring, without saying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That's what he done.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And if he wanted to take a town that was far from the border, with a [? descent, ?] he dropped.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know what the [? descent ?] mean.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He put-- he dropped the army [? with the descent, ?] with airplanes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And when I was coming home-- I finished work Friday afternoon-- I finished work, I come home, Chelm was bombed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Chelm [INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Street ?] was bombed, destroyed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Three people got killed already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And on Saturday-- on Sunday, we hear on the radio what the Germans doing to the Yiddish people in these places where it occupied.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The best Yiddish peoples-- lawyers, doctors, solicitors, actors, writers, the rabbis-- they have to clean the toilet, the public toilets and sweeping-- sweeping the streets.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They built special places to hang people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They took some people, the best people from the town-- from each town-- and they hang them in middle from the city, like in [?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Elizabeth ?] or something like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they forced the-- the people from the town to go and have a look at the hanged people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they tell the people, if you will be naughty, you will finish up like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You mean [? what you mean. ?] If your will be against.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How you like that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So how did your life change?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What did you--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What change?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never changed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After this day, I went to Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because after German start occupied from the west, Russian Army went, occupied Poland from the east.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they start occupying, occupying, occupying one town after the other.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
